Scavenger
Core Class Card

Health: 3 Strikes

Defenses
- Improvised Cover (junk, crates, debris)
- When hit with a Strike of damage, roll a d6. On a 5+, you avoid it by ducking behind cover.
- When a Strike would kill you, roll a d6. On a 6, you scrape by with nothing but a scar.

Boons
- Keen Eye: Once per room, ask the GM: "What here can I use or steal?" and get a truthful answer.
- Resourceful: When using a scavenged or improvised item, roll +1d6 and keep the highest.

